<br>
I personally love my Iksar Necro.  Pensfan likes his Forehead.<br>
All necro class have pro's and cons.  Mana pool is great for the Foreheads but they dont have fantastic life regen without uber items. Level 60+ iksar necromancers are very few and far spread altho they can out regen any other class of necro hands down.<br>
<br>
I say this as im finding out now.  from lvl 44 on the leveling grind is alot slower than with my Gnome.  Figure this, for every 5 yellow of exp gained an Iksar Necro needs to gain 6 yellow of experince, or for every 100% EXP gained and Iksar need to gain 120%...<br>
<br>
If you want to be in the Toon for the long haul then Iksar IMHO is the way to go(if you have the gear).  If you want to dink around with a necro then pick the gnome as they level the fastest.<br>
