<br>
Level 8<br>
Spell: Dark Pact<br>
Effect:  Decreases Hit points by 4 per tic / increases Mana by 4 per tic (Tic=6 seconds) <br>
<br>
With all necromancer races except iksars you will lose 2 hit points every 6 seconds while sitting. You will lose 3 hit points while standing. <br>
<br>
No hit points are lost while Iksars are sitting.  Iksars will lose 2 hit points every 6 seconds while standing.<br>
<br>
Hit point Regeneration from level 1 to 19<br>
Iksars 2hp standing 4hp sitting / other races 1hp standing 2hp sitting<br>
<br>
